reviewText:
Bought as a birthday gift for 3 year old grandson who is crazy for Spongebob.
Happy to let Amazon do the shipping for me.

sponge bob movies are a great way to keep grandchildren (or children if you're not as old as I am) happy and occupied while doing things that need them to be away from underfoot (fixing supper, cleaning, etc.) the children enjoy watching them and there is very little violence or obsenity in any of them!
i bought it for my girls 10 and 15.i don't know if my son 18 years old saw it.but the girls loved it and watch it over and over.they say any spongebob fan would love it.
What's not to like about spongebob
I love Spongebob! He, Squidward, Patricks and all of the other characters are funny! This is a great DVD! Thanks Amazon!
Funny and I love SpongeBob! All the episodes are great! Good to watch for a good chuckle and fun for kids of all ages even if you are all "grown " up!
Fun to watch. What can I say,how about : this guy rocks for the little guys and some grown ups too.
My grandson LOVES SpongeBob so this was the ideal gift for him.  After watching it MANY times, it is still a cute movie.

My daughter is two years old and absolutely loves spongebob she watches nothing but sponge bob and dr suess movies. She sings sponge bobs name around the house ans talks about how she loves sponge bob. Such a good show untill you've seen the same episodes 50 times in a row in one day.
My son laughed so much watching this that I had to buy it for him along with a few slide whistles for him and his cousins.
my daughter loves spongebob and every now and then we will sit down together pop in one of the movies and watch it
